# QA Testing Checklist

- [ ] Check `.env` configuration
- [ ] Start dev server
- [ ] Run QA Flow 1: Registration and Setup
- [ ] Run QA Flow 2: POS Hero Path (Categories, Inventory, Cash Checkout, Credit Checkout)
- [ ] Run QA Flow 3: Roles and Permissions (Register Seller, Assign Role, Verify Access)
- [ ] Document any errors in `QA_REPORT.md`
